<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vestingMembers[_address].totalSum == 0 || block.number <= vestingMembers[_address].start [7827,7915]" label="vestingMembers[_address].totalSum == 0 || block.difficulty <= vestingMembers[_address].start" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: block.number >= vestingMembers[_address].end [7963,8007]" label="block.difficulty >= vestingMembers[_address].end" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vestingMembers[_address].totalSum         .mul(block.number - vestingMembers[_address].start)         .div(vestingMembers[_address].end - vestingMembers[_address].start)         .sub [8132,8314]" label="vestingMembers[_address].totalSum         .mul(block.difficulty - vestingMembers[_address].start)         .div(vestingMembers[_address].end - vestingMembers[_address].start)         .sub" />
</actions>
